            </p>
          </div>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="fw-bold">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-handshake me-3" style="color: #fe424d"></i
              >Introduction and Acceptance
            </h2>
            <p>
              Welcome to WanderLust, a demonstration project that simulates an
