              <strong>Please note:</strong> As this is a demonstration project,
              these terms are for illustrative purposes only and do not
              constitute a legally binding agreement.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="fw-bold">
              <i
                class="fa-solid fa-map-location-dot me-3"
                style="color: #fe424d"></i
              >Use of WanderLust
            </h2>
            <p>In this demonstration project:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>
                You may view and interact with simulated listings and reviews
              </li>
              <li>You may create an account and manage your profile</li>
              <li>
                You may create and manage demonstration listings and reviews
              </li>
              <li>
                You understand that all functionalities are for demonstration
                purposes only
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              Any content you create within the WanderLust demo is intended for
              testing and demonstration purposes only. In a real application,
              users would be required to provide accurate, lawful, and
              non-infringing content.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="fw-bold">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-user-shield me-3" style="color: #fe424d"></i
              >Account Responsibility
            </h2>
            <p>While using the WanderLust demo, you may:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>
                Create a demo account with a username, email, and password
              </li>
              <li>Sign in using OAuth providers like Google or GitHub</li>
              <li>Maintain the security of your account credentials</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              <strong>Remember:</strong> As this is a demonstration project, we
              recommend not using sensitive or personal passwords that you use
              for other services.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="fw-bold">
              <i
                class="fa-solid fa-scale-balanced me-3"
                style="color: #fe424d"></i
              >Limitations of Liability
            </h2>
            <p>
              The WanderLust demo project is provided "as is," without warranty
