              <li>Data may be reset or deleted periodically</li>
              <li>
                We are not liable for any loss or damage arising from your use
                of this demo application
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              This project is not intended for production use or for storing
              sensitive personal information.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="fw-bold">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-ban me-3" style="color: #fe424d"></i
              >Termination and Suspension
            </h2>
            <p>For demonstration purposes, we reserve the right to:</p>
            <ul>
