              <li>Remove any content or accounts for any or no reason</li>
              <li>Modify or discontinue the service without notice</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              As this is a non-commercial project, all features and content are
              subject to change or removal as the project evolves.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="fw-bold">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-comments me-3" style="color: #fe424d"></i
              >Contact and Feedback
            </h2>
            <p>
              This project was created by Anuraj Jit Saikia (Raja) as a
